# Testing rules

- After **backend** changes: `.\scripts\test.ps1 -Layer api`
- After **frontend component** changes: `.\scripts\test.ps1 -Layer unit`
- After **UI flow** changes: `.\scripts\test.ps1 -Layer e2e`
- Before finishing any task: `.\scripts\test.ps1 -Layer all`
- Add tests with new features (see AGENTS.md)
- Tests must use `APP_ENV=test`; never depend on the developer's real media library
- Load the matching skill from `.cursor/skills/verify-*` for detailed steps
